Package: projectr
Type: Package
Title: Creates and organises project directories
Version: 0.0-7
Date: 2011-05-01
Author@R: person("Richard", "Cotton", email = "richierocks@gmail.com")
Author: Richard Cotton
Maintainer: Richard Cotton <richierocks@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.0.0), utils
Description: Helps you maintain consistency in file locations across projects, by allowing functional access to directories.  For example, if you specify that your project should have a data directory with location "Data", then a function data_dir will be created returning that location.
License: Unlimited
LazyLoad: yes       
LazyData: yes
